  "local_port": 41058,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best side jobs to get on the weekend to earn extra cash?",
  "response": "There are several side jobs you can consider for earning extra cash on weekends. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Freelancing:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Writing, graphic design, web development, digital marketing.\n   - **Platforms:** Upwork, Fiverr, Freelancer.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Flexible hours, work from home, variety of tasks.\n\n2. **Ride-Sharing:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Driving, good customer service.\n   - **Platforms:** Uber, Lyft.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Flexible hours, potential for good earnings, especially during peak times.\n\n3. **Food Delivery:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Driving or biking, good customer service.\n   - **Platforms:** DoorDash, Uber Eats, Grubhub.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Flexible hours, high demand, work during meal times.\n\n4. **Tutoring:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Expertise in a subject, teaching ability.\n   - **Platforms:** Wyzant, Tutor.com, or directly through local schools and colleges.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Flexible hours, high demand, satisfying work helping others.\n\n5. **Pet Sitting/Dog Walking:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Love for animals, reliability.\n   - **Platforms:** Rover, Wag.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Flexible hours, enjoyable for animal lovers, good pay.\n\n6. **Event Staffing:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Customer service, ability to work in a fast-paced environment.\n   - **Platforms:** Local event staffing agencies.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Can be fun, good pay, often includes weekends.\n\n7. **Handyman Services:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Basic home repair skills, reliability.\n   - **Platforms:** TaskRabbit, Thumbtack.\n   - **Why It's Good:** High demand, good pay, flexible hours.\n\n8. **Babysitting:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Experience with children, patience.\n   - **Platforms:** Care.com, Sittercity.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Flexible hours, good pay, rewarding work.\n\n9. **Market Research:**\n   - **Skills Needed:** Willingness to share opinions, basic internet skills.\n   - **Platforms:** Swagbucks, Survey Junkie.\n   - **Why It's Good:** Can be done from home, easy to fit into your schedule.\n\n10. **Crafts and Art Sales:**\n    - **Skills Needed:** Creative skills in arts or crafts.\n    - **Platforms:** Etsy, local markets.\n    - **Why It's Good:** Turn your hobby into income, potential for good profits.\n\nWhen choosing a side job, consider your skills, interests, and the flexibility you need. This will help you find a job that not only brings in extra cash but also fits well into your lifestyle.",
